com.learningtree.crs471

Class Recording

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.learningtree.crs471.Recording
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MusicRecording

    public abstract class Recording
extends Object
implements Comparable
    This class represents a Recording. It describes the recording title, price, category, imageName and running time.

    Subclasses must implement the method getRunningTime() to return the total running time for the recording.

    Author:
    471 Development Team
